 class HsqlMaxValueIncrementer
          Class to increment maximum value of a given HSQL table with the equivalent of an auto-increment column (note : if you use this class, your HSQL key column should NOT be auto-increment, as the sequence table does the job)
The sequence is kept in a table; there should be one sequence table per table that needs an auto-generated key.
 class MySQLMaxValueIncrementer

The sequence is kept in a table; there should be one sequence table per table that needs an auto-generated key.
 class OracleSequenceMaxValueIncrementer
          Class to retrieve the next value of a given Oracle SEQUENCE If the cacheSize is set then we will retrive that number of values from sequence and then serve the intermediate values without querying the database
